WEBVTT

00:00:01.102 --> 00:00:04.050
PROFESSOR? HELLO?
IT'S ME... LAZAR!

00:00:04.050 --> 00:00:06.153
I KNOW YOU'RE
IN HERE. WE NEED
YOUR HELP

00:00:06.153 --> 00:00:07.186
WITH
THE NEXT DUEL.

00:00:07.186 --> 00:00:08.625
YOU EVER THINK
ABOUT REDECORATING,

00:00:08.625 --> 00:00:10.645
MAYBE SOME
TRACK LIGHTING?

00:00:10.645 --> 00:00:13.432
THE DARKNESS HELPS
WITH MY PREPARATION.

00:00:13.432 --> 00:00:16.090
AND AS A FAITHFUL
SERVANT OF ILIASTER,

00:00:16.090 --> 00:00:18.250
I KNOW THE DARKNESS CAN
ONLY BE ILLUMINATED

00:00:18.250 --> 00:00:19.864
BY THE DRAGON STAR.

00:00:19.864 --> 00:00:21.070
HOW MAY I BE OF SERVICE?

00:00:21.070 --> 00:00:22.708
I'M SO GLAD
THAT YOU ASKED.

00:00:22.708 --> 00:00:25.110
DIRECTOR GOODWIN
NEEDS YOUR
HYPNOTIC POWERS

00:00:25.110 --> 00:00:27.269
TO TAP INTO
THE MIND OF
A POSSIBLE SIGNER.

00:00:27.269 --> 00:00:29.650
HE THANKS YOU
FOR THROWING
YOUR FIRST DUEL

00:00:29.650 --> 00:00:31.462
TO END UP IN
THE LOSER'S BRACKET,

00:00:31.462 --> 00:00:33.944
BUT NOW HE NEEDS
YOU TO PERFORM.

00:00:33.944 --> 00:00:35.435
WHOM SHALL I DUEL?

00:00:43.644 --> 00:00:46.280
♪ GOING FAST
MAKES ME FEEL ALIVE ♪

00:00:46.280 --> 00:00:50.317
♪ MY HEART BEATS
IN HYPER DRIVE ♪

00:00:50.317 --> 00:00:53.387
♪ DO YOU THINK YOU CAN WIN
ONLY IF I LOSE? ♪

00:00:53.387 --> 00:00:56.056
♪ JUST LET DESTINY CHOOSE ♪

00:00:56.056 --> 00:00:58.725
♪ I CAN HEAR YOU BREATHING ♪

00:00:58.725 --> 00:01:01.361
♪ I CAN SEE YOU COMING ♪

00:01:01.361 --> 00:01:02.963
♪ I CAN FEEL THE WIND ♪

00:01:02.996 --> 00:01:07.234
♪ IT'S BLOWING ME AROUND ♪

00:01:07.234 --> 00:01:10.337
♪ TAKE A SHOT AT ME
RUNNIN' SIDE BY SIDE ♪

00:01:10.337 --> 00:01:13.206
♪ IT'S A BLUR AS I GO BY ♪

00:01:13.206 --> 00:01:15.776
♪ I CAN HEAR YOU BREATHING ♪

00:01:15.776 --> 00:01:18.478
♪ I CAN SEE YOU COMING ♪

00:01:18.478 --> 00:01:20.714
♪ I CAN FEEL THE WIND ♪

00:01:20.714 --> 00:01:23.016
♪ IT'S BLOWING ME AROUND ♪

00:01:23.016 --> 00:01:26.486
♪ SEE THE SUN A-RISIN' ♪

00:01:26.486 --> 00:01:28.355
♪ FIRE IN THE SKY ♪

00:01:28.355 --> 00:01:33.760
♪ GREATNESS THRUSTS ITSELF
INTO OUR LIVES ♪

00:01:41.768 --> 00:01:43.570
[CROWD CHEERS]

00:01:43.570 --> 00:01:46.073
YUSEI BEAT HUNTER!

00:01:46.073 --> 00:01:47.441
YEAH! LOOKS LIKE
HE'S MOVING ON

00:01:47.441 --> 00:01:48.609
TO THE SEMI-FINALS.

00:01:48.609 --> 00:01:49.610
OH, MAN! I WISH I
COULD BE DOWN THERE

00:01:49.610 --> 00:01:52.179
AND DUEL HIM.

00:01:52.179 --> 00:01:53.947
HE'S GOOD. BUT YUSEI
LEARNED HIS BEST MOVES

00:01:53.981 --> 00:01:55.649
FROM YOURS TRULY.

00:01:55.649 --> 00:01:57.951
OH? AND WHERE
WERE THOSE MOVES

00:01:57.985 --> 00:02:00.320
WHEN YOU LOST IN
THE FIRST ROUND?

00:02:00.320 --> 00:02:02.756
HUH? HEH HEH.

00:02:02.756 --> 00:02:05.959
WAIT! I WAS PLAYING
AS YOU, WHICH MEANS
THAT YOU LOST!

00:02:05.993 --> 00:02:06.994
AS FAR AS THE MILLIONS
OF PEOPLE WATCHING,

00:02:06.994 --> 00:02:09.229
I DIDN'T LOSE A THING.

00:02:09.229 --> 00:02:11.565
THAT'S THE LAST
TIME YOU DUEL AS ME!

00:02:11.565 --> 00:02:13.600
Announcer:
WE HAVE A SPECIAL ANNOUNCEMENT!

00:02:13.600 --> 00:02:17.104
YES. THE RUMORS YOU
HEARD ARE TRUE!

00:02:17.104 --> 00:02:18.205
LISTEN UP, FIRST-ROUND
LOSERS!

00:02:18.205 --> 00:02:20.240
DON'T HEAD
FOR THE EXITS JUST YET!

00:02:20.240 --> 00:02:22.309
REX GOODWIN, OUR MASTER
OF CEREMONIES,

00:02:22.309 --> 00:02:25.946
HAS SET UP A LOSER'S BRACKET
FOR THE FIRST ROUND.

00:02:25.979 --> 00:02:28.382
THAT MEANS IF YOU LOST,
GRAB YOUR DECK,

00:02:28.382 --> 00:02:30.584
BECAUSE YOU MIGHT GET A SECOND
CHANCE TO DUEL AGAIN.

00:02:30.584 --> 00:02:34.221
[CROWD CHEERS]

00:02:34.221 --> 00:02:37.124
ALL RIGHT! MY FORTUNE
CUP'S NOT OVER YET!

00:02:37.124 --> 00:02:38.425
UM, TECHNICALLY...

00:02:38.425 --> 00:02:40.327
SAVE YOUR "TECHNICALLY"
FOR THE BLOGS, DEX!

00:02:40.327 --> 00:02:43.597
UH, WHAT DEX MEANS IS
MY NAME IS UP THERE.

00:02:48.368 --> 00:02:50.537
Yusei, thinking:
WHAT ARE YOU
UP TO, GOODWIN?

00:02:50.537 --> 00:02:53.206
YOU'RE NOT
THE TYPE WHO
GIVES SECOND CHANCES

00:02:53.206 --> 00:02:55.442
UNLESS YOU'RE
GOING TO GET
SOMETHING OUT OF IT.

00:02:58.412 --> 00:03:00.681
[HUMMING]

00:03:00.681 --> 00:03:02.349
NOW, JUST YOU WATCH!

00:03:02.349 --> 00:03:05.419
I'M GONNA WIN FOR
CERTAIN THIS TIME,
LUNA! HEH HEH.

00:03:05.419 --> 00:03:06.753
I NEED YOUR HAIR
BRAIDS THOUGH, OK?

00:03:06.753 --> 00:03:08.488
GET YOUR OWN!

00:03:08.488 --> 00:03:09.756
COME ON, LUNA!

00:03:09.756 --> 00:03:11.258
OH!

00:03:11.258 --> 00:03:13.393
NOW TAKE YOUR SEATS.

00:03:13.393 --> 00:03:15.195
WE'RE ABOUT TO GIVE
TWO OF THESE DUELISTS
ANOTHER OPPORTUNITY.

00:03:15.195 --> 00:03:18.765
FIRST, WE DREW TWO
VERY LUCKY PLAYERS.

00:03:18.765 --> 00:03:20.801
AND I ASSURE YOU IT
WAS RANDOM, OK?

00:03:20.801 --> 00:03:22.202
AND FIRST UP IS...

00:03:22.202 --> 00:03:25.605
EVERYONE'S FAVORITE
GREEN-HAIRED GIRL.

00:03:25.605 --> 00:03:27.607
SHE'S FAST, SHE'S FEISTY,

00:03:27.607 --> 00:03:30.644
AND SHE HAS TO BE
HOME BEFORE HER BEDTIME.

00:03:30.644 --> 00:03:34.281
GIVE IT UP FOR
THE NEXT GENERATION OF
DUELING SUPERSTARS.

00:03:34.281 --> 00:03:39.453
LADIES AND GENTLEMAN, I
PRESENT TO YOU MISS LUNA!

00:03:39.453 --> 00:03:40.454
HUH?

00:03:57.892 --> 00:04:00.494
Yusei:
LUNA'S DUELING?

00:04:00.494 --> 00:04:02.763
I'M GUESSING
THEY FINALLY GOT
THE RIGHT KID

00:04:02.763 --> 00:04:04.365
FOR THE MATCH, HUH?

00:04:04.365 --> 00:04:05.466
YOU KNOW, BY THE END OF
THE DUEL WE HAD,

00:04:05.466 --> 00:04:08.535
I DIDN'T THINK THE BOY
WAS HALF BAD.

00:04:08.535 --> 00:04:10.671
I CAN'T WAIT TO SEE
WHAT HIS SISTER'S GOT.

00:04:15.509 --> 00:04:16.777
I CAN'T DUEL!

00:04:16.777 --> 00:04:17.778
CAN'T DUEL?
BUT, LUNA,

00:04:17.778 --> 00:04:18.779
IT WAS YOUR NAME
ON THAT INVITATION.

00:04:18.779 --> 00:04:20.514
YOU BELONG HERE.

00:04:20.514 --> 00:04:23.517
BUT I'M HER.
SHE CAN'T GO OUT
THERE AND DUEL!

00:04:23.517 --> 00:04:26.921
LEO, I'M AFRAID THAT
THE JIG IS UP, YOUNG MAN.

00:04:26.921 --> 00:04:29.490
THE CROWD WANTS
YOUR SISTER.

00:04:29.490 --> 00:04:31.358
[CROWD CHANTING "LUNA!"]

00:04:31.358 --> 00:04:34.461
I CAN'T! YOU GUYS
DON'T UNDERSTAND.

00:04:34.461 --> 00:04:37.665
SOMETHING STRANGE HAPPENS
TO ME WHENEVER I DUEL.

00:04:37.665 --> 00:04:39.099
OH, NOT AGAIN!

00:04:39.133 --> 00:04:40.334
ARE YOU GONNA START
THAT STUFF

00:04:40.334 --> 00:04:41.869
ABOUT DUEL SPIRITS?

00:04:41.869 --> 00:04:43.604
YOU'RE GETTING
A LITTLE TOO OLD TO
PLAY MAKE BELIEVE.

00:04:43.604 --> 00:04:45.372
IT'S NOT MAKE BELIEVE.

00:04:45.372 --> 00:04:47.841
AND IF THE ONLY WAY
TO PROVE IT IS
BY GOING OUT THERE,

00:04:47.841 --> 00:04:49.310
WELL, THEN I GUESS
I'LL HAVE TO GO
OUT THERE AND DUEL.

00:04:49.310 --> 00:04:51.879
OK, BUT IF
YOU WIN, I GET
TO BE YOU

00:04:51.879 --> 00:04:53.347
FOR THE NEXT
ROUND!

00:04:53.347 --> 00:04:54.715
WOW. THANKS FOR
YOUR SUPPORT, LEO.

00:04:57.518 --> 00:05:01.322
[CROWD CHEERS]

00:05:01.322 --> 00:05:03.424
GOOD LUCK, LUNA!

00:05:03.424 --> 00:05:05.092
NOW, LEO, WHAT'S THIS
ABOUT YOUR SISTER HEARING

00:05:05.092 --> 00:05:06.093
DUEL SPIRITS?

00:05:06.093 --> 00:05:08.195
OH, IT'S NOTHING.

00:05:08.195 --> 00:05:09.463
YOU SURE?

00:05:09.463 --> 00:05:10.864
MM-HMM. SHE
ALWAYS DOES THIS!

00:05:10.864 --> 00:05:13.834
WE'LL BE DUELING,
AND THEN SHE'S
ALL, LIKE, THIS:

00:05:13.834 --> 00:05:14.902
[IMITATING LUNA]
"I FEEL FUNNY.
HEAR THAT?

00:05:14.902 --> 00:05:16.637
IT'S DUEL SPIRITS!"

00:05:16.637 --> 00:05:18.639
[REGULAR VOICE]
SHE'S JUST AFRAID
I'LL BEAT HER.

00:05:18.639 --> 00:05:19.640
I'VE SEEN SOME
WEIRD STUFF AND...

00:05:19.640 --> 00:05:22.409
OH, COME ON!

00:05:22.409 --> 00:05:24.611
IF THAT WERE
TRUE THEN, WELL,
I DON'T KNOW,

00:05:24.611 --> 00:05:26.246
BUT LUNA WOULD
BE A WHOLE LOT
MORE IMPORTANT

00:05:26.246 --> 00:05:27.414
THAN SHE IS!

00:05:30.684 --> 00:05:34.388
SO TELL ME WHY
YOU THINK SHE'S
A SIGNER, GOODWIN.

00:05:34.388 --> 00:05:36.590
WELL, FOR STARTERS,

00:05:36.590 --> 00:05:38.726
THE D-TECTOR PICKED
HER OUT OF THE CROWD.

00:05:38.726 --> 00:05:39.860
TRUST ME.

00:05:39.860 --> 00:05:40.861
SHE'S A LOT MORE IMPORTANT
THAN ANYONE KNOWS,

00:05:40.861 --> 00:05:43.397
EVEN HER OWN BROTHER.

00:05:43.397 --> 00:05:45.199
ONCE SHE DUELS
THE PROFESSOR,

00:05:45.199 --> 00:05:47.167
THEN WE'LL KNOW
WITHOUT A DOUBT.

00:05:47.167 --> 00:05:49.436
LET'S SEE IF ZIGZIX
IS READY TO MONITOR HER.

00:05:49.436 --> 00:05:52.673
♪ GOIN' FAST MAKES
ME FEEL ALIVE ♪

00:05:52.673 --> 00:05:53.874
♪ MY HEARTBEAT'S... ♪

00:05:53.874 --> 00:05:55.642
HUH? OH, DIRECTOR!

00:05:55.642 --> 00:05:57.511
ZIGZIX REPORTING
FOR DUTY, SIR!

00:05:57.511 --> 00:05:59.313
JUST LOOK AT THIS!

00:05:59.313 --> 00:06:01.382
IF THE NEEDLE
EXCEEDS THIS
YELLOW SECTION,

00:06:01.382 --> 00:06:03.283
THERE'S NO DOUBT
OUR LITTLE LUNA
IS A SIGNER!

00:06:03.283 --> 00:06:04.785
AND MORE SIGNERS MEAN
MORE ENERGY.

00:06:04.785 --> 00:06:06.220
MORE ENERGY
MEANS MORE ENER-D.

00:06:06.220 --> 00:06:07.654
AND THEN WE'LL
HAVE ENOUGH TO...

00:06:07.654 --> 00:06:10.691
HE REALLY NEEDS
TO GET OUT MORE.

00:06:10.691 --> 00:06:11.759
NOW, THERE'S
ANOTHER REASON THAT
WE'VE BEEN STUDYING

00:06:11.759 --> 00:06:14.228
THIS LITTLE GIRL.

00:06:14.228 --> 00:06:15.796
EIGHT YEARS AGO,
SHE WAS ADMITTED

00:06:15.796 --> 00:06:17.131
TO A SPECIAL
HOSPITAL, SAYING

00:06:17.164 --> 00:06:19.266
THAT SHE COULD HEAR
DUEL SPIRIT VOICES.

00:06:19.266 --> 00:06:21.935
SO SHE HAS QUITE
THE IMAGINATION.

00:06:21.935 --> 00:06:23.871
IT'S A LITTLE MORE
COMPLICATED THAN THAT.

00:06:26.306 --> 00:06:28.308
JACK, SHE WAS
A DUELING PRODIGY,

00:06:28.308 --> 00:06:29.710
AND BEATING OUR
GREATEST PROFESSIONALS

00:06:29.710 --> 00:06:31.779
AT THE AGE OF 3.

00:06:31.779 --> 00:06:34.314
THEN ONE DAY, SHE SUDDENLY
COLLAPSED DURING A DUEL

00:06:34.314 --> 00:06:36.250
AND FELL INTO A COMA.

00:06:36.250 --> 00:06:38.485
NO ONE KNOWS WHY,
NOT EVEN THE BEST
DOCTORS.

00:06:38.485 --> 00:06:41.655
IN FACT, THERE WAS ONLY
ONE PERSON WHO BELIEVED

00:06:41.655 --> 00:06:43.724
THAT SHE'D
WAKE UP AGAIN,

00:06:43.724 --> 00:06:45.726
AND THAT WAS HER
TWIN BROTHER LEO.

00:06:45.726 --> 00:06:47.327
AND THEN FOR
NO APPARENT REASON,

00:06:47.327 --> 00:06:50.397
SHE WOKE UP HEALTHY
A MONTH LATER.

00:06:50.397 --> 00:06:51.765
THAT'S
A GREAT MOVIE OF
THE WEEK, GOODWIN,

00:06:51.765 --> 00:06:53.534
BUT WHO CARES?

00:06:53.534 --> 00:06:56.370
YOU SHOULD CARE,
MR. ATLAS.

00:06:56.370 --> 00:06:57.905
WHAT GOT
OUR ATTENTION

00:06:57.905 --> 00:06:59.440
WAS WHAT SHE SAID
WHEN SHE WOKE UP.

00:06:59.440 --> 00:07:00.574
SHE SAID THAT SHE
WASN'T ASLEEP.

00:07:00.574 --> 00:07:03.277
SHE SAID SHE SPENT
THAT ENTIRE MONTH

00:07:03.277 --> 00:07:05.179
IN THE DUEL MONSTERS
SPIRIT WORLD.

00:07:05.179 --> 00:07:07.614
AND I'M A BLUE-EYES
WHITE DRAGON.

00:07:07.614 --> 00:07:08.749
COME ON, NOW.

00:07:08.749 --> 00:07:10.617
FUNNY. BUT WE HAVE
REASON TO BELIEVE

00:07:10.617 --> 00:07:12.486
SHE TOLD THE TRUTH.

00:07:12.486 --> 00:07:16.190
FOR INSTANCE, SHE
KNEW OF THE ANCIENT
DRAGON STAR LEGEND.

00:07:16.190 --> 00:07:19.293
IN FACT, SHE KNEW
SOME THINGS THAT
EVEN WE DID NOT...

00:07:19.293 --> 00:07:22.396
VITAL CLUES TO
UNLOCKING THE MYSTERY

00:07:22.396 --> 00:07:24.531
OF THE PEOPLE
OF THE STARS

00:07:24.531 --> 00:07:25.566
AND MORE,

00:07:25.566 --> 00:07:26.600
LIKE THE INCREDIBLE POWER

00:07:26.600 --> 00:07:28.435
OF THE ANCIENT
CRIMSON DRAGON.

00:07:32.139 --> 00:07:34.942
BUT A FEW DAYS
AFTER WAKING,

00:07:34.942 --> 00:07:37.444
HER MEMORY BEGAN
TO FADE, LIKE IT
WAS A DREAM.

00:07:37.444 --> 00:07:38.946
AND NOW SHE
REMEMBERS NOTHING
OF THE SPIRIT WORLD,

00:07:38.946 --> 00:07:41.815
LEAVING US ONE CHOICE:

00:07:41.815 --> 00:07:43.484
TO MAKE HER DUEL AND GO
BACK TO THAT WORLD.

00:07:43.484 --> 00:07:46.954
ONLY THEN
WILL WE LEARN IF
SHE IS A SIGNER.

00:07:48.655 --> 00:07:50.324
AND WITH HER HELP...

00:07:50.324 --> 00:07:51.525
WE CAN UNLEASH
THE CRIMSON DRAGON

00:07:51.525 --> 00:07:55.662
SO THAT WE CAN SAVE
OUR TROUBLED WORLD.

00:07:55.662 --> 00:07:58.632
Announcer:
NOW ENTERING THE ARENA...

00:07:58.632 --> 00:08:04.438
THE LITTLE DUELIST WHO COULD,
THE PINT-SIZED PRODIGY, LUNA!

00:08:04.438 --> 00:08:06.406
Luna, thinking:
OK, LUNA, NOTHING
TO WORRY ABOUT.

00:08:06.406 --> 00:08:08.175
JUST THE BIGGEST DUEL
OF YOUR LIFE

00:08:08.175 --> 00:08:10.177
ON NATIONAL TELEVISION.

00:08:10.177 --> 00:08:13.180
HUH. I WONDER
IF YUSEI'S WATCHING.

00:08:15.415 --> 00:08:16.717
Announcer:
AND NOW, HER OPPONENT...

00:08:16.717 --> 00:08:19.486
THE DEAN OF THE DECK,
THE BRAIN OF THE GAME...

00:08:19.486 --> 00:08:21.588
THE PROFESSOR!

00:08:21.588 --> 00:08:23.190
HE'S GOT A Ph.D. IN PSYCHOLOGY,

00:08:23.190 --> 00:08:25.125
HYPNO-LOGY AND DUEL-OLOGY,

00:08:25.159 --> 00:08:27.628
SO LUNA BETTER LOOK OUT!

00:08:44.578 --> 00:08:47.314
PLEASED TO MEET YOU,
DEAR LUNA.

00:08:47.314 --> 00:08:49.616
UM... HI.

00:08:49.616 --> 00:08:52.819
I'VE HEARD MANY
THINGS ABOUT YOU.

00:08:52.819 --> 00:08:54.388
I'M SURE THIS DUEL WILL
BE QUITE ILLUMINATING

00:08:54.388 --> 00:08:57.357
FOR THE BOTH OF US,
DON'T YOU THINK?

00:08:57.357 --> 00:08:58.825
Luna, thinking:
DOUBT IT.

00:08:58.825 --> 00:09:00.327
[KURIBON CALLS]

00:09:00.327 --> 00:09:01.895
HUH? KURIBON!

00:09:01.895 --> 00:09:04.264
WHY DON'T YOU
EVER TALK WHEN
LEO'S AROUND?

00:09:04.264 --> 00:09:05.365
NOW LET'S GET DUELING!

00:09:10.204 --> 00:09:12.873
Announcer: REMEMBER,
ONLY THE WINNER ADVANCES.

00:09:12.873 --> 00:09:14.208
THE LOSER IS OUT FOR GOOD.

00:09:14.208 --> 00:09:17.211
LET'S DUEL!
LET'S DUEL.

00:09:17.211 --> 00:09:19.279
LIKE THE BLOOMING LOTUS,
YOU MAY GO FIRST.

00:09:19.279 --> 00:09:20.614
SURE. FINE.

00:09:20.614 --> 00:09:23.784
I DRAW...

00:09:23.784 --> 00:09:26.853
AND I SUMMON
SUNNY PIXIE
IN DEFENSE MODE.

00:09:26.853 --> 00:09:28.956
[SUNNY PIXIE CHUCKLES]

00:09:32.893 --> 00:09:34.928
AW. A FAIRY?
THAT'S ADORABLE!

00:09:34.928 --> 00:09:35.929
KEEP IT UP, LUNA!

00:09:35.929 --> 00:09:39.233
YOUR TURN,
PROFESSOR.

00:09:39.233 --> 00:09:42.703
AND I LOOK FORWARD
TO IT. THANK YOU.

00:09:42.703 --> 00:09:47.174
I SUMMON A UNIQUE
MONSTER KNOWN AS
SYMMETRY RORSCHACH.

00:09:53.180 --> 00:09:55.048
Luna, thinking:
THAT CARD WON'T
LET ME FOCUS.

00:10:09.529 --> 00:10:10.797
LUNA, THINK OF
MY RORSCHACH AS
IF IT WERE

00:10:10.797 --> 00:10:14.231
A PUDDLE OF RAIN OR
A DROP OF INK IN A LAKE.

00:10:14.231 --> 00:10:16.266
LOOK AT IT, AND TELL
ME WHAT YOU SEE.

00:10:16.266 --> 00:10:19.169
TELL ME IF IT REMINDS
YOU OF ANYTHING.

00:10:19.169 --> 00:10:22.305
LOOK INTO YOUR FEARS,
YOUR DREAMS,

00:10:22.305 --> 00:10:25.308
EVEN MEMORIES LOST
LONG AGO.

00:10:25.308 --> 00:10:28.145
WHAT DO YOU SEE WHEN
YOU GAZE INTO THE ABYSS?

00:10:28.145 --> 00:10:30.213
A FRIEND, PERHAPS?
YOUR FAMILY?

00:10:30.213 --> 00:10:31.281
OR MAYBE
A FAR-OFF PLACE,

00:10:31.281 --> 00:10:33.750
DIMMING LIKE
THE CANDLE OF TIME.

00:10:33.750 --> 00:10:36.119
I...I SEE...

00:10:36.119 --> 00:10:37.621
YES, TELL ME, LUNA.

00:10:37.621 --> 00:10:40.223
WHAT DO YOU SEE?

00:10:40.223 --> 00:10:42.559
I DON'T KNOW.

00:10:42.559 --> 00:10:44.327
LOOK CLOSE...

00:10:46.563 --> 00:10:49.266
CLOSE...

00:10:49.266 --> 00:10:50.534
CLOSE...

00:10:50.534 --> 00:10:52.102
WHAT DO YOU SEE?

00:10:52.102 --> 00:10:53.470
IT'S A CRYSTAL SKULL,
I THINK!

00:10:53.470 --> 00:10:55.038
A MOTH.

00:10:55.038 --> 00:10:56.540
Leo, thinking:
THIS PROFESSOR'S

00:10:56.540 --> 00:10:57.974
A FEW CARDS SHORT
OF A DUEL DECK.

00:10:58.008 --> 00:11:00.644
WHAT'S HE DOING
TO LUNA?

00:11:00.644 --> 00:11:03.513
Professor:
LOOK CLOSE, LUNA.

00:11:03.513 --> 00:11:04.581
CLOSE...

00:11:04.581 --> 00:11:08.552
LOOK CLOSELY...

00:11:08.552 --> 00:11:10.453
WHAT DO YOU SEE, LUNA?

00:11:10.453 --> 00:11:13.156
UM, I SEE...

00:11:15.492 --> 00:11:18.428
A FAIRY?

00:11:26.570 --> 00:11:27.804
[SCREAMS]

00:11:27.804 --> 00:11:29.239
Professor:
WHAT DO YOU SEE?

00:11:29.239 --> 00:11:30.707
[LUNA SCREAMING]

00:11:37.364 --> 00:11:40.066
LIKE THE CATERPILLAR
WHO SECLUDES
ITSELF IN DARKNESS

00:11:40.066 --> 00:11:41.067
BEFORE BECOMING
A BUTTERFLY,

00:11:41.067 --> 00:11:44.070
YOU MUST FACE
YOUR FEARS.

00:11:44.070 --> 00:11:47.340
YOU MUST FACE
YOUR MEMORIES AND LIVE
THROUGH THEM AGAIN.

00:11:47.340 --> 00:11:48.575
DO NOT BE SCARED.

00:11:48.575 --> 00:11:50.177
BUT I'M AFRAID.

00:11:50.177 --> 00:11:52.479
YOU MUST BE BRAVE
ENOUGH TO RELIVE

00:11:52.479 --> 00:11:53.680
WHAT HAPPENED
MANY YEARS AGO.

00:11:53.680 --> 00:11:56.550
I KNOW YOU HAVE
GREAT POWER, DEAR LUNA.

00:11:56.550 --> 00:11:58.785
I KNOW THAT YOU HEAR
THE DUEL SPIRITS.

00:11:58.785 --> 00:12:01.154
THE OTHERS MAY NOT
BELIEVE YOU, BUT I DO.

00:12:01.154 --> 00:12:02.222
I'LL HELP YOU RETURN
TO THAT PLACE...

00:12:02.222 --> 00:12:05.158
THE DUEL MONSTERS
SPIRIT WORLD.

00:12:05.158 --> 00:12:06.426
YES, IT WAS ALL REAL

00:12:06.426 --> 00:12:09.462
AND NOT SOME FIGMENT OF
YOUR IMAGINATION, LUNA.

00:12:09.462 --> 00:12:11.198
I'M...

00:12:11.198 --> 00:12:13.266
I'M STARTING
TO REMEMBER,
PROFESSOR.

00:12:13.266 --> 00:12:14.901
I KNOW YOU ARE.

00:12:14.901 --> 00:12:16.903
BUT FOR OUR NEXT STEP,
YOU NEED TO TRUST ME, LUNA.

00:12:16.903 --> 00:12:18.038
CAN YOU DO THAT?

00:12:18.038 --> 00:12:20.140
I NEED...

00:12:20.140 --> 00:12:22.409
I NEED YOU
TO WANT TO RETURN TO
THE DUEL SPIRIT WORLD.

00:12:22.409 --> 00:12:24.411
I NEED YOUR PROMISE, LUNA.

00:12:24.411 --> 00:12:26.580
I PROMISE, PROFESSOR.

00:12:26.580 --> 00:12:28.381
TAKE ME BACK.

00:12:28.381 --> 00:12:31.484
VERY GOOD.
NOW FOLLOW
MY INSTRUCTIONS.

00:12:31.484 --> 00:12:34.020
WHEN SYMMETRY RORSCHACH
DISPATCHED OF YOUR FAIRY,

00:12:34.020 --> 00:12:35.488
ITS SPECIAL
ABILITY CONTINUED.

00:12:35.488 --> 00:12:38.225
WOULD YOU KINDLY TURN OVER
THE TOP CARD OF YOUR DECK

00:12:38.225 --> 00:12:39.226
AND REVEAL IT?

00:12:44.531 --> 00:12:46.666
[KURIBON CALLS]

00:12:46.666 --> 00:12:48.368
KURIBON!

00:12:48.368 --> 00:12:50.270
THANK YOU FOR
IDENTIFYING YOUR MONSTER.

00:12:50.270 --> 00:12:52.305
HE WILL BE MOST HELPFUL

00:12:52.305 --> 00:12:55.375
FOR THE NEXT STAGE OF
OUR LITTLE EXPERIMENT.

00:12:55.375 --> 00:12:57.677
NOW I NEED YOU
TO THINK BACK
TO THAT SCARY TIME

00:12:57.677 --> 00:12:59.112
WHEN YOU WERE
IN YOUR COMA.

00:12:59.112 --> 00:13:01.748
TRY TO REMEMBER.

00:13:01.748 --> 00:13:04.150
Luna, thinking:
I'VE TRIED BEFORE,
BUT I CAN'T.

00:13:04.150 --> 00:13:06.019
THERE'S NOTHING I
REMEMBER FROM IT.

00:13:06.019 --> 00:13:07.654
LUNA!

00:13:07.654 --> 00:13:09.990
LUNA, WAKE UP!

00:13:09.990 --> 00:13:12.392
OHH. I'M REMEMBERING.

00:13:15.996 --> 00:13:18.098
LEO, YOU LOOK SICK.

00:13:18.098 --> 00:13:20.667
I'M WORRIED
ABOUT LUNA, DEX.

00:13:20.667 --> 00:13:22.569
WHAT'S HE DOING?

00:13:22.569 --> 00:13:24.537
I PLACE TWO CARDS
FACEDOWN.

00:13:24.537 --> 00:13:26.539
IT'S YOUR TURN.

00:13:26.539 --> 00:13:28.508
DON'T BE SCARED,
LUNA.

00:13:30.777 --> 00:13:31.778
I DRAW...

00:13:31.778 --> 00:13:36.049
AND I SUMMON OUT
KURIBON.

00:13:39.519 --> 00:13:41.154
Computer: KURIBON IS

00:13:41.154 --> 00:13:42.722
A LEVEL ONE LIGHT ATTRIBUTE
FAIRY-TYPE MONSTER

00:13:42.722 --> 00:13:44.991
WITH 300 ATTACK POINTS

00:13:44.991 --> 00:13:47.427
AND 200 DEFENSE POINTS.

00:13:47.427 --> 00:13:49.029
THAT'S PERFECT.

00:13:49.029 --> 00:13:50.130
I PLAY MY FACEDOWN.

00:13:50.130 --> 00:13:53.199
IT IS KNOWN AS
LIGHT TO THE DEPTHS.

00:13:53.199 --> 00:13:55.101
LIKE THE NORTHERN STAR,

00:13:55.101 --> 00:13:58.271
THIS LIGHT ILLUMINATES
THE PATH INSIDE OF YOU.

00:13:58.271 --> 00:14:00.740
NOW, SEND THE TOP FIVE
CARDS ON YOUR DECK

00:14:00.740 --> 00:14:02.242
TO THE GRAVEYARD,

00:14:02.242 --> 00:14:05.178
THEN REVEAL THE SIXTH CARD,
ADDING IT YOUR HAND.

00:14:05.178 --> 00:14:07.314
AND YOU MUST PLAY
THAT CARD

00:14:07.314 --> 00:14:09.215
AS CERTAIN AS
THE PATH OF LIGHT ITSELF,

00:14:09.215 --> 00:14:11.918
OR SUFFER 2,000 POINTS
OF DAMAGE.

00:14:11.918 --> 00:14:14.154
NOW, THEN,
WHY DON'T WE BEGIN?

00:14:14.154 --> 00:14:16.389
LISTEN TO MY VOICE AS
I COUNT THEM OFF.

00:14:16.389 --> 00:14:20.026
AND... 1.

00:14:20.026 --> 00:14:21.194
PERFECT.

00:14:21.194 --> 00:14:23.630
2...

00:14:23.630 --> 00:14:25.565
3...

00:14:25.565 --> 00:14:28.168
4...

00:14:28.168 --> 00:14:30.270
5...

00:14:30.270 --> 00:14:32.038
AND 6.

00:14:32.038 --> 00:14:33.039
WONDERFUL.

00:14:33.039 --> 00:14:35.141
NOW SHOW ME.

00:14:35.141 --> 00:14:36.910
WHAT'S THE CARD YOU'RE
HOLDING IN YOUR HAND?

00:14:40.313 --> 00:14:42.615
AH. AS I HAD HOPED,

00:14:42.615 --> 00:14:45.251
THE FIELD SPELL...
ANCIENT FOREST.

00:14:45.251 --> 00:14:47.120
YOU WILL USE IT.

00:14:47.120 --> 00:14:50.123
THIS FOREST IS QUITE
A SPECIAL PLACE.

00:14:50.123 --> 00:14:52.258
ALL MONSTERS ARE
SWITCHED TO ATTACK MODE,

00:14:52.258 --> 00:14:54.694
AND NEITHER OF US
CAN SUMMON OR SWITCH
A MONSTER TO DEFENSE.

00:14:54.694 --> 00:14:57.063
EVEN IF YOU WERE TO ATTACK,

00:14:57.063 --> 00:14:58.732
YOUR MONSTER
WOULD BE DESTROYED

00:14:58.732 --> 00:15:00.200
ONCE THE BATTLE
WAS OVER.

00:15:00.200 --> 00:15:01.735
HA HA HA.

00:15:01.735 --> 00:15:03.770
SOME SAY THIS FOREST
RESEMBLES

00:15:03.770 --> 00:15:05.138
SOMEPLACE ELSE.

00:15:05.138 --> 00:15:07.941
FIGHTING FORBIDDEN,
SECRETS REVEALED,

00:15:07.941 --> 00:15:09.676
WHY, IT'S JUST LIKE
THE SPIRIT WORLD.

00:15:09.676 --> 00:15:10.677
TAKE US THERE NOW.

00:15:10.677 --> 00:15:13.546
WE HAVE WORK TO DO.

00:15:33.748 --> 00:15:35.750
WHERE AM I?

00:15:35.750 --> 00:15:36.951
[FAIRIES LAUGHING]

00:15:42.590 --> 00:15:44.058
[LUNA CHUCKLES]

00:15:46.761 --> 00:15:52.566
Luna, thinking: KURIBON!
WHERE IS THIS PLACE?

00:15:52.566 --> 00:15:56.137
IT LOOKS SO FAMILIAR,
BUT I CAN'T REMEMBER.

00:15:56.137 --> 00:15:59.040
[KURIBON CALLS]

00:15:59.040 --> 00:16:01.542
I SENSE THAT THIS IS
A SAFE PLACE,

00:16:01.542 --> 00:16:03.678
BUT SOMETHING FEELS WRONG.

00:16:05.313 --> 00:16:08.549
Professor: EXCELLENT.

00:16:08.549 --> 00:16:10.718
LUNA HAS
FINALLY TRAVELED
TO THE SPIRIT WORLD.

00:16:10.718 --> 00:16:13.788
NOW I WILL TRULY TEST
HER SIGNER POWERS.

00:16:13.788 --> 00:16:14.922
[CHUCKLES]

00:16:14.922 --> 00:16:16.791
MY TURN.

00:16:16.791 --> 00:16:18.159
AND I'LL BE
ACTIVATING

00:16:18.159 --> 00:16:20.828
MY FACEDOWN GESTALT TRAP.

00:16:20.828 --> 00:16:22.997
AND THIS PARTICULAR TRAP CARD

00:16:22.997 --> 00:16:24.832
WILL EQUIP
ON YOUR LITTLE KURIBON.

00:16:26.734 --> 00:16:29.603
LET'S SEE HOW LUNA
DEALS WITH THIS.

00:16:29.603 --> 00:16:32.106
NOT ONLY ARE KURIBON'S
ABILITIES CANCELED,

00:16:32.106 --> 00:16:34.275
BUT ALL HIS POINTS,
BOTH ATTACK AND DEFENSE,

00:16:34.275 --> 00:16:38.212
GO TO ZERO, DEAR LUNA.

00:16:38.212 --> 00:16:39.647
[KURIBON CALLS]

00:16:41.916 --> 00:16:45.119
KURIBON, WHAT
JUST HAPPENED?!

00:16:45.119 --> 00:16:48.022
THE TREES AREN'T
DEAF, BUT THEY ARE MUTE

00:16:48.022 --> 00:16:50.458
TO YOUR CRYING PLEAS.

00:16:50.491 --> 00:16:54.028
I EQUIP IMMORTAL
HOMEOSTASIS ON KURIBON.

00:16:54.028 --> 00:16:56.864
NOW HE CANNOT
BE DESTROYED IN BATTLE.

00:16:56.864 --> 00:16:58.265
BUT SADLY
HIS FATE IS WORSE,

00:16:58.265 --> 00:17:01.769
FOR NOW HE SERVES
AS THE ARCHITECT
OF YOUR LOSS.

00:17:01.769 --> 00:17:04.638
HIS ORIGINAL ATTACK POINTS
HAVE BEEN ALTERED.

00:17:04.638 --> 00:17:07.274
AND UNTIL THEY
CAN FINALLY BE
RESTORED, YOU SUFFER.

00:17:07.274 --> 00:17:09.777
300 POINTS A ROUND,

00:17:09.777 --> 00:17:12.613
MUCH LIKE THE ILL-TEMPERED
DOG WHO BITES YOUR HAND,

00:17:12.613 --> 00:17:14.982
WHETHER YOU BRING
FOOD OR FOUL.

00:17:14.982 --> 00:17:18.452
NEXT I SACRIFICE
SYMMETRY RORSCHACH.

00:17:18.486 --> 00:17:20.121
AND WITH THAT REMOVED,

00:17:20.121 --> 00:17:24.525
I CAN SUMMON
IDO THE SUPREME
MAGICAL FORCE.

00:17:26.927 --> 00:17:29.463
[GROWLING]

00:17:34.769 --> 00:17:36.170
Computer: WHENEVER
THE MONSTER CARD,

00:17:36.170 --> 00:17:37.171
IDO THE SUPREME MAGICAL FORCE,

00:17:37.171 --> 00:17:39.473
IS DESTROYED,

00:17:39.507 --> 00:17:40.508
IT IS RESUMMONED TO YOUR FIELD

00:17:40.508 --> 00:17:44.011
AT THE END OF THE TURN.

00:17:44.011 --> 00:17:45.112
[CALLS]

00:17:45.112 --> 00:17:48.649
DON'T WORRY. HUH?

00:17:48.649 --> 00:17:49.650
[GROWLING]

00:17:52.520 --> 00:17:54.155
[SCREAMING]

00:17:54.155 --> 00:17:55.156
Professor: EVEN THOUGH
IDO WILL BE DESTROYED

00:17:55.156 --> 00:17:57.058
IF I ATTACK WITH HIM,

00:17:57.058 --> 00:18:00.895
HE STILL RETURNS
TO MY FIELD AT
THE END OF EVERY TURN.

00:18:00.895 --> 00:18:03.464
OF COURSE, WITH
HIM SUMMONED, THOUGH,

00:18:03.497 --> 00:18:06.734
NO OTHER MONSTERS WILL
BE ALLOWED ON MY FIELD.

00:18:06.734 --> 00:18:09.136
A SMALL PRICE TO PAY.

00:18:12.006 --> 00:18:13.741
WAKE UP, LUNA!

00:18:13.741 --> 00:18:15.643
SHE'S JUST
STANDING THERE!

00:18:15.643 --> 00:18:17.645
COULD THIS BE IT?

00:18:17.645 --> 00:18:20.014
IS SHE TOO SCARED TO DUEL?

00:18:26.053 --> 00:18:28.622
WHAT'S WRONG?

00:18:28.622 --> 00:18:30.558
IDO THE SUPREME
MAGICAL FORCE,

00:18:30.558 --> 00:18:32.126
ATTACK KURIBON!

00:18:32.126 --> 00:18:35.129
AND BRING OUT LUNA'S
MARK OF THE DRAGON.

00:18:36.864 --> 00:18:37.898
[KURIBON CALLING]

00:18:49.743 --> 00:18:51.145
NO!

00:18:55.983 --> 00:18:57.885
OF COURSE,
WITH KURIBON
STILL EQUIPPED

00:18:57.885 --> 00:19:00.020
WITH MY LITTLE SPELL,

00:19:00.020 --> 00:19:02.723
HE ISN'T DESTROYED
BUT SURVIVES.

00:19:02.723 --> 00:19:05.292
AND NEXT ROUND,
HE'LL BE DESTROYED
AND SURVIVE AGAIN

00:19:05.292 --> 00:19:07.828
AND AGAIN UNTIL YOU
GIVE ME WHAT I NEED.

00:19:07.828 --> 00:19:09.630
THINK, LUNA.

00:19:09.630 --> 00:19:10.865
THINK.

00:19:10.865 --> 00:19:11.999
THINK ABOUT THE SPIRIT WORLD.

00:19:11.999 --> 00:19:16.170
THINK ABOUT WHAT
WAS REVEALED TO YOU.

00:19:16.170 --> 00:19:17.905
THINK ABOUT
THE CRIMSON DRAGON.

00:19:17.905 --> 00:19:19.607
THINK.

00:19:21.542 --> 00:19:23.611
THINK.

00:19:23.611 --> 00:19:25.012
THINK.

00:19:25.012 --> 00:19:26.680
THINK.

00:19:26.680 --> 00:19:29.917
TELL ME ABOUT
THE CRIMSON DRAGON!

00:19:34.221 --> 00:19:36.690
NO! THIS WORLD'S
SUPPOSED TO BE
A SAFE PLACE.

00:19:36.690 --> 00:19:37.691
YOU CAN'T HARM ME HERE!

00:19:51.672 --> 00:19:54.074
BUT... BUT HOW DID
THAT HAPPEN?

00:19:55.976 --> 00:19:57.878
DID YOU FORGET ALREADY?

00:19:57.878 --> 00:19:59.980
IDO RETURNS TO MY FIELD
WHENEVER IT'S DESTROYED.

00:19:59.980 --> 00:20:02.449
HA HA HA.

00:20:02.483 --> 00:20:04.218
IT'S YOUR TURN, LUNA.

00:20:04.218 --> 00:20:06.020
AND DON'T NEGLECT ALL
THE PROGRESS WE'VE MADE.

00:20:06.020 --> 00:20:09.623
I DRAW.

00:20:09.623 --> 00:20:12.459
REMEMBER, YOU LOSE
300 POINTS

00:20:12.493 --> 00:20:15.262
DUE TO THE EFFECT OF
IMMORTAL HOMEOSTASIS.

00:20:15.262 --> 00:20:17.932
PERHAPS THIS WILL
JOG YOUR MEMORY.

00:20:17.932 --> 00:20:19.133
[LUNA SCREAMING]

00:20:27.675 --> 00:20:31.278
I SUMMON MY MONSTER,
SUNLIGHT UNICORN.

00:20:33.614 --> 00:20:34.815
[SUNLIGHT UNICORN NEIGHING]

00:20:37.718 --> 00:20:41.021
AND NOW I EQUIP
HORN OF THE UNICORN

00:20:41.021 --> 00:20:43.257
ON MY SUNLIGHT
UNICORN.

00:20:49.730 --> 00:20:51.465
Professor, thinking:
HOW'S SHE FIGHTING BACK?

00:20:51.498 --> 00:20:53.567
WHO'S GIVING
HER STRENGTH?

00:21:01.675 --> 00:21:03.177
[MOANS]

00:21:03.177 --> 00:21:04.979
OHH.

00:21:04.979 --> 00:21:06.814
[NEIGHING]

00:21:08.282 --> 00:21:10.451
SUNLIGHT UNICORN?

00:21:11.785 --> 00:21:14.588
[FEMALE VOICE]
LUNA. LUNA.

00:21:14.588 --> 00:21:17.791
WHO IS IT?
WHO'S OUT THERE?

00:21:17.791 --> 00:21:20.961
LUNA, YOU HAVE
FINALLY RETURNED

00:21:20.961 --> 00:21:23.464
TO FULFILL YOUR PROMISE.

00:21:23.464 --> 00:21:24.665
WHAT PROMISE?

00:21:24.665 --> 00:21:28.202
TO PROTECT THE REALM
OF THE DUEL SPIRITS

00:21:28.202 --> 00:21:31.972
FROM THE FORCES OF EVIL.

00:21:31.972 --> 00:21:35.976
BUT I'M JUST A LITTLE KID!
WHAT CAN I DO?

00:21:35.976 --> 00:21:37.678
[FEMALE VOICE]
YOU CAN COME WITH ME.

